description: Full planning application for development comprising a mixed use scheme for 231 residential units (Class C3) ranging from 3 to 23 storeys in height, 1333 sq.m of shopping, financial and professional services, restaurants and cafes (Classes A1, A2 and A3), alterations to the highway and ancillary parking and landscaping facilities and services.
borough: London Borough of Barking and Dagenham
